{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/132/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Gatsby Starter Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b25ba483-5d97-5189-af90-db7b77bb56f8","excerpt":"옷가게 할인 받기 https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120818 변수 구매한 옷의 가격 price 제한사항 10 ≤ price ≤ 1,000,000 price는 10원 단위(1의 자리가…","html":"<h3>옷가게 할인 받기</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120818\">https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120818</a></p>\n<h4>변수</h4>\n<p>구매한 옷의 가격 price</p>\n<h4>제한사항</h4>\n<p>10 ≤ price ≤ 1,000,000<br>\nprice는 10원 단위(1의 자리가 0)<br>\n소수점 이하를 버린 정수를 반환</p>\n<h4>풀이</h4>\n<p>조건문을 통해서 price의 할인 조건을 확인 후 할인된 가격을 반환하는 방식으로 풀었다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>price >= 500000 확인, 맞으면 price * 8 / 10에서 소수점 이하를 버린 값을 반환</li>\n<li>price >= 300000 확인, 맞으면 price * 9 / 10에서 소수점 이하를 버린 값을 반환</li>\n<li>price >= 100000 확인, 맞으면 price * 95 / 100에서 소수점 이하를 버린 값을 반환</li>\n<li>조건을 모두 만족하지 않으면 price를 반환</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>코드</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">price</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">trunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>price <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">500000</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> price <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> price <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">300000</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> price <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">9</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> price <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100000</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> price <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">95</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> price<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"옷가게 할인 받기","date":"March 31, 2023","description":"https://school.programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/120818"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/131/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"아이스 아메리카노"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/133/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"개미 군단"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b25ba483-5d97-5189-af90-db7b77bb56f8","previousPostId":"826bf1a4-a3d6-542c-b973-a1b034724ccd","nextPostId":"09fa2ebd-69ab-540d-a86a-688b0335869c"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}